            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based, <strong>hob-safe</strong> <strong>oven-proof casserole dish </strong>with a matching lid with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-low heat</p><p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice</strong>, <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and the <strong>remaining tamari soy sauce</strong> to the pot and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-15-1693312626382-x200.jpg",
