            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-15-1693312626382-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>with 225ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 18-20 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
