      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the rice is cooked, stir the <strong>spinach</strong> through until wilted and give everything a good mix up  – this is your <strong>hoisin rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
