    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, top the <strong>hoisin rice </strong>with the <strong>sweet</strong> <strong>sesame chicken thighs & charred pepper</strong></p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>toasted sesame seeds </strong>over the chicken and drizzle over any<strong> remaining juices</strong> from the chicken</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
